Hello! I'm hakunamatata.HakunaMatata, a task list chat box
You can key in your tasks and I'll keep track of them for you.
There are three types of tasks I'm able to keep track of.
Todo: use "todo + description" to create (e.g. todo taskInfo).
Deadline: use "deadline + description + /by + date" to create (e.g. deadline taskInfo /by June 6th).
Event: use "event + description + /at + date" to create (e.g. event taskInfo /at Mon 2-4pm).
You can also use "list" to check the recorded tasks.
Or use "done + task index" to mark the task as done.
